name: TaxCut 2008 Tax Return
summary: Learn about .T08 files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: TaxCut files use the extension "TXX," where "XX" is the tax year being filed. For example, .T07 files are for the 2007 tax year.
NOTE: TaxCut was re-branded as "H&R Block At Home" for the 2009 tax year. Data from T08 files may still be imported into At Home 2009.

description: Tax return file created by TaxCut 2008, a program that allows users to create U.S. federal and state tax returns for the 2008 tax year; contains tax forms and their fields that have been filled in by the user; can be printed or e-filed using TaxCut 2008.
